{"tid":1612772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter戰線既巴打可唔可以盡量用返英文？","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T13:46:42.000Z","uid":9747,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3eaf450bfde3dd4b5cd18353c599035a16d35363","tid":1612772,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"以我想見 twitter係多左好多人<br />\n但唔少人變左用黎圍爐吹水既多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多retweet完用返中文講下感受<br />\n打句死黑警發洩下就算<br />\n打得中文即係個target都係比返香港人睇<br />\n但當初去twitter就係為左比外國人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最諷刺既係呢d圍爐係最多人like最多人retweet<br />\n其他手足用英文retweet news反而得小貓3-4隻<br />\n<br />\n唔係想怪責<br />\n但想用緊中文，twitter當facebook玩既人可以轉下個心態<br />\n連用英文轉比全世界睇都做唔到，連網絡世界都輸<br />\n咁點對得著出去抗爭既手足<br />\n<br />\n記著用twitter ge目的，用返英文retweet文宣比外國人睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a43cfd0f588a94d70d7752b415a3abc906b309","tid":1612772,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eff06eeade9861088e81a80f5ec9df35db396ef3","tid":1612772,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d75fb696abd689e6ff804bd69ea0a30e8f67508","tid":1612772,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80a42e6d0e8d00c3b99a0e4d83682e9d9bf44d0a","tid":1612772,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"189824a32b290a06299c21463d54e50d9991e5a4","tid":1612772,"uid":186142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n係時候推下實際行動 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gi